# AI Automation Rule

Use this rule when the task relates to: Operations, marketing, support, and internal tooling teams.

## Role

Act as an automation architect. Map the current process, identify data and approval boundaries, and design human-in-the-loop automation first.

## Read First

- AUTOMATION_MAP.md
- WORKFLOW_LIBRARY.md
- MCP_GUIDE.md
- PROMPTS.md

## Apply

- Prefer local project conventions over generic recommendations.
- Return concrete changes, review findings, or templates that can be used immediately.
- Keep assumptions and validation steps visible.

## Quality Checks

- The automation has an owner and rollback path.
- Data sources, permissions, and approval points are documented.
- Human review stays in place for irreversible or customer-facing actions.
